reviews.review_text: The Walrus Yes, another night with tanks...  oh boy, Bruce sang part of Jack Straw, Grand piano in cue brought back memories of Keith.  nice set list great sound.   1 thing I remember more than anything was Jerry's solo on Candyman...  Was it the gooney birds or just me?

Beware the Soapium KC losers ripping off the masses, my friend bought some of this so-called hash, we dubbed it soapium. Threw it away after one session. Graphics tasted like that junk for a year.
Great show, KOA was a mess, drive to Denver was a riot
